OL,3,CCheshire council fined after man
OL,4,Ckilled by fallen tree
OL,6,FCheshire East Council has been fined
OL,7,F#500,000 after 'the most amazing man'
OL,8,Fwas killed by a falling tree.
OL,10,FChristopher Hall, 48, from Wilmslow,
OL,11,Fwas walking his dog in The Carrs ` one
OL,12,Fof the town's parks ` on 28 August
OL,13,F2020, when the large limb of a tree
OL,14,Ffell and struck him. He received
OL,15,Fmultiple injuries and sadly died at
OL,16,Fthe scene.
