OL,6,FLess than a year before, another large
OL,7,Flimb from the same tree had fallen off
OL,8,Fbut the incident was never
OL,9,Finvestigated by the council or its
OL,10,Fground maintenance company Ansa
OL,11,FEnvironmental Services Limited.
OL,13,FAs the District Judge sentenced both
OL,14,Fat Chester Magistrates Court on 8
OL,15,FNovember 2024 he said that the
OL,16,Fprevious incident should have "acted
OL,17,Fas a wake-up call".
OL,19,FIn a victim personal statement,
OL,20,FChris's wife Fiona said her husband
OL,21,F"loved life and life loved him".
