OL,6,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,7,FSafety Executive (HSE) found that when
OL,8,Fsame tree had shed another large limb
OL,9,Fin September 2019, no investigation
OL,10,Fwas carried out by those responsible
OL,11,Fto assess whether the tree posed a
OL,12,Ffuture safety risk. The council, who
OL,13,Fcontrolled the park, did not have a
OL,14,Fformal overarching tree strategy to
OL,15,Fmanage the risks from trees in public
OL,16,Fplaces, and their grounds services
OL,17,Fcontractor, Ansa Environmental
OL,18,FServices Limited, had no robust tree
OL,19,Fmanagement policy.
