OL,6,FIn his own statement, Chris's son Sam
OL,7,Fspoke about the impact his dad's death
OL,8,Fhas had on his life. "For the past
OL,9,Ffour years, it's felt like a long,
OL,10,Fpainful trail ` a path we never wanted
OL,11,Fto be on," he said. "Losing dad was
OL,12,Flosing my life and strength. I miss
OL,13,Fevery little piece of him ` his
OL,14,Flaughter, wisdom, and adventures we
OL,15,Fshared.
