OL,6,F"Our travels ignited a passion in me,
OL,7,Fbut now every journey feels
OL,8,Fbittersweet without him. I've taken up
OL,9,Fdiving, which was one of his dreams
OL,10,Ffor us. Being underwater helps me
OL,11,Fconnect with him."
OL,13,FCheshire East Council pleaded guilty
OL,14,Fto breaching Section 3(1) of the
OL,15,FHealth and Safety at Work Act 1974.
OL,16,FThey were fined #500,000 and ordered
OL,17,Fto pay #7,284 costs at a hearing at
OL,18,FChester Magistrates Court on 8
OL,19,FNovember 2024.
