OL,6,FThere was no separate penalty for Ansa
OL,7,FEnvironmental Services Limited of
OL,8,FMiddlewich, Cheshire, who also pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty to breaching 3(1) of the Health
OL,10,Fand Safety at Work Act 1974. They were
OL,11,Fordered to pay a nominal fine of #500.
OL,12,FIn passing his sentence, the District
OL,13,FJudge said it would have been
OL,14,Fdisproportionate to impose fines on
OL,15,Fboth.
OL,17,FHSE inspector Lorna Sherlock said:
OL,18,F"This was an utterly tragic event that
OL,19,Fhas caused the death of a much-loved
OL,20,Fhusband and father.
